node.text: Due to Covid19, @humelake Christian Camps is unfortunately closed. However, that doesn’t stop us from getting a Summer Camp experience! @humelake is having a virtual camp hosted at Camp Kajabe! Tune in every day this week or next on YouTube to watch a time of worship, sermons, and some fun at Camp Kajabe! You might just see me talking about the importance of the local church and how God gave us the amazing ability to organize and live with other Christ followers! I’ll see you guys on the virtual camp! 🌲🏕🌲 #humelake #campkajabe #humeathome #humelakechristiancamps

node.text: After years of training, dozens of losses, and literally almost dying… I finally won Kajabe at @humelake! Whether its my high school camper days or being a counselor for years to come, this will always be the game that I will die for. 🏕 #humelake #kajabe #ponderosa #churchcamp
